               <msContents>
                  <summary/>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3034RepCh314">Lǝssāna sabʾ</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡ ናሁ፡
                        ተማኅፀ<supplied reason="omitted">ን</supplied>ኩ፡ <choice>
                           <sic>በኆኅታተ፡</sic>
                           <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">በኆኅያተ፡</corr>
                        </choice>
                        ስምከ፡ ካዊ፡ ወበቀዳማይ፡ ይውጣ፡ ዘጥንተ፡ ፊደሉ፡ አሌፍ፡ ከመ፡ ታድኅነኒ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እምትሣኤ፡ ልሳን፡ ወአፍ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        እግዚእየ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዕቀቦ፡ ወአድኅኖ፡ 
                           <sic>እምልሳነ፡</sic>
                         ለገብርከ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚእ፡ እምልሳነ፡ ዘመድ፡ ወባዕድ፡ ወእምልሳነ፡ ብእሲት፡ ወብእሲ፡
                        ወእምልሳነ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ውሉደ፡ አዳም፡ ወሔዋን፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11697WaldaEg">Walda ʾƎgziʾ</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula at the
                        end of the text.</note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4697MagicPr">Ṣalot baʾǝnta māʾśaromu la-ʾagānǝnt</title>
                     
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ማ<supplied reason="omitted">እ</supplied>ሠሮሙ፡
                        ለአጋንንት፡ ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ ሰዳዴ፡ አጋንንት፡ ፋኑኤል፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ እምጽርሁ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይስክዩ፡ እለ፡ ይኔስሑ፡ <choice>
                           <sic>ለጌጋይ፡</sic>
                           <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ለጌጋየ፡</corr>
                        </choice>
                        ዚአሁ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        
                           <sic>ኦአምላከ፡</sic>
                         ፋኑኤል፡ አድ<supplied reason="omitted">ኅ</supplied>ኖ፡ እመናግንቲሁ፡ 
                           <sic>ለሰይጠን፡</sic>
                        
                        ወእመሥገርቱ፡ ለዲያብሎስ፡ ለገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚእ፡ <add place="interlinear">ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም፡</add> እስመ፡ አልቦ፡ ነገር፡ ዘይሰዓኖ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ወገፁ፡ ዘፍጹም፡
                        በጽልመት፡ ፈርሃ፡ ወደንገፀ፡ ዲያብሎስ፡ ርእዮ፡ ብሁተ፡ ልደት፡ በሥጋ፡ አምላ<supplied reason="omitted">ከ</supplied>፡ በሲኦል።
                     </explicit>
                     <note>Cp. <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/DWH75H4R"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Worrell1909Zauberwesen"/><title level="a">Studien zum abessinischen Zauberwesen</title><title level="j">Zeitschrift für Assyriologie und verwandte Gebiete</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">William Hoyt</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Worrell</t:surname></author><date>1909</date><biblScope unit="volume">23</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">149-183</biblScope><note type="url">http://menadoc.bibliothek.uni-halle.de/dmg/periodical/titleinfo/118117</note><citedRange>176f.</citedRange></bibl>.
                        The name of the owner <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11697WaldaEg">Walda ʾƎgziʾ</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula at the
                        end of the text. The name of a later owner, <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11698KidanaMa">Kidāna Māryām</persName>, is added above the line.
                     </note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4698MagicPr">Ṣalot baʾǝnta ʾǝda sabʾ ʾǝkkuyān</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ 
                           <sic>እጅ</sic>
                        
                        ሰብእ፡ እኩያን፡ እንትልን፡ እንትልን፡ እንትልን፡ እንትልን፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ወአውገዝኩክሙ፡ አጋንንት፡ ጸዋጋን፡ ወመናፍ<supplied reason="omitted">ስት</supplied>፡ ርኩሳን፡ ከመ፡ ኢትቅረቡ፡ ኀበ፡ ነፍሱ፡ ወሥጋሁ፡ ወኀበ፡ ደቂቁ፡ ወሰብአ፡
                        <choice>
                           <sic>ቢቱ፡</sic>
                           <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ቤቱ፡</corr>
                        </choice>
                        <choice>
                           <sic>ወእንስሳሀ፡</sic>
                           <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ወእንስሳሁ፡</corr>
                        </choice>
                        ለገብረ፡ <choice>
                           <sic>እግዚአብሒር፡</sic>
                           <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">እግዚአብሔር፡</corr></choice>
                         ወልደ፡ እግዚእ፡
                        <add place="interlinear">ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም፡</add>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11697WaldaEg">Walda ʾƎgziʾ</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula at the
                        end of the text. The name of a later owner, <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11698KidanaMa">Kidāna Māryām</persName>, is added above the line.
                     </note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4699MagicPr">Protective prayer for the dissolution of the spells</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                        
                           <sic>ፍትሕ፡</sic>
                         ሥራያተ፡
                        ወመቋጽራተ፡ 
                           <sic>እምለዕለ፡</sic>
                         ገብርከ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚእ፡ ጥትጥኛኛ፡ ጥትጥኛኛ፡ ጥትጥኛኛ፡ ጥትጥኛኛ፡ ጥትጥኛኛ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        መሃይምን፡ ወመሐይም<supplied reason="omitted">ና</supplied>ት፡ ካህን፡ ወካህናት፡ ዲያቆን፡ ወዲያቆናት፡ ንጉሥ፡ ወነገሥት፡ 
                           <sic>ጰጰስ፡</sic>
                        
                        ወጳጳሳት፡ 
                           <sic>ቂሰ፡</sic>
                         ወቆሞስ፡ ዘተደ<supplied reason="omitted">ግ</supplied>መ፡ በላዕለ፡ ገብርከ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚእ፡
                        <add place="interlinear">ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም፡</add>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11697WaldaEg">Walda ʾƎgziʾ</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula at the
                        end of the text. The name of a later owner, <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11698KidanaMa">Kidāna Māryām</persName>, is added above the line.
                     </note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4700MagicPr">Ṣalota fatāḥe śǝrāyāt</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                        
                           <sic>ጸሎት፡</sic>
                         ፈታሔ፡
                        ሥራያት፡ እምላዕለ፡ ገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚእ፡ መየው፡ መየው፡ መየው፡ መየው፡ መየው፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ከመ፡ ተፍትሐ፡ መዋቅሕቲሁ፡ 
                           <sic>ለጰውሎስ፡</sic>
                         ከማሁ፡ ፍታሕ፡ መዋቅሕቲሁ፡ ወሥራያቲሁ፡ ለገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚእ፡ ለዓለመ፡
                        <supplied reason="omitted">ዓለም፡</supplied>
                        
                           <sic>አሚን፡</sic>
                         ወአሜን፡ <add place="unspecified">ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም፡</add>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11697WaldaEg">Walda ʾƎgziʾ</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula at the
                        end of the text. The name of a later owner, <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11698KidanaMa">Kidāna Māryām</persName>, is added in another hand.
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>

